		}

		}

			var referrerDomain = document.referrer ? document.referrer.split('/')[2] : null;
			if (domain === referrerDomain) {
				document.getElementById('goBack').href = document.referrer;
			} else {
				document.getElementById('goBack').href = '/';
			}
		})
	</script>
